name: Nancy E. MAZZARELLI v. Oswald A. MAZZARELLI

parties: Nancy E. MAZZARELLI v. Oswald A. MAZZARELLI.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiff’s motion to affirm the decree of the Family Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is assigned to the motion calendar for oral argument.
WEISBERGER, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Howard I. Lipsey, Providence, for plaintiff.

Nancy E. MAZZARELLI v. Oswald A. MAZZARELLI.
No. 80-567-A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
July 23, 1981.
Howard I. Lipsey, Providence, for plaintiff.
Oswald A. Mazzarelli, pro se.
